OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early morning mist, fog and
OL,6,Flow cloud in the east will clear
OL,7,Fquickly after sunrise. Another bright
OL,8,Fand sunny day expected with
OL,9,Ftemperatures slightly higher than
OL,10,FThursday. Winds turning much lighter
OL,11,Fthrough the day.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA clear night to come with
OL,14,Fhigh cloud in the south. Patchy mist
OL,15,Fand fog developing in prone spots to
OL,16,Fthe east. A grass frost developing in
OL,17,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
